pageContext.claim: “The Democrats are just, as always, looking for trouble. They do nothing constructive, even in times of crisis. They don't want to blame their cash cow, China, for the plague. China is blaming Europe. Dr. Fauci will be testifying before the Senate very soon!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump blocked Fauci from testifying in the House of Representatives. He has no basis to claim China is a "cash cow" for Democrats. Trump regularly praised China for its responses to the coronavirus until the death toll soared in the United States.
